    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH index below 1.0 for all geometric variants confirms acceptability relative to predicate device.",
